attributes.Long form description: The student assembles the table, first assembles and screws the hex socket heads of the legs to the shelf using the Allen wrench, then aligns the top table with the legs to assemble and screw them together, and finally makes sure the hex heads are tight using the Allen wrench.

attributes.Action sentence: The student screws the first leg onto the shelf.

attributes.Incorrect Action Explanation: The student fails to insert the allen wrench.
The student drops the allen wrench by accident.
The student drops the hex socket head by accident.

attributes.Action sentence: The student screws the second leg onto the shelf.

attributes.Incorrect Action Explanation: The student drops the allen wrench by accident.

attributes.Action sentence: The student screws the third leg of the shelf.

attributes.Incorrect Action Explanation: The student fails to screw the hex socket head.

attributes.Action sentence: The student screws the fourth leg onto the shelf.
The student screws the legs of the table to the top tray.
